reviewText: I have seen this movie, being that it was given to me by the wonderful young man that made this movie with his freinds.  He is an exceptional storyteller, and the actors are INCREDIBLE!!!!  It is academy award worthy.  I so enjoyed this movie, i watched it a thousand times!! You will love it.  But then i lost it,- i was devestated.  Needless to say i am purchasing it again, plus an extra copy!!
